            "bgtext": "#ffffff",
            "subtitle": "Why We Exist",
            "title": "Our Mission",
            "size_text": "h3",
            "text": "",
            "answer_content": "<p>We built Quity because we believe every Australian deserves straightforward, judgement-free access to proven smoking cessation treatments. Smoking remains one of the leading causes of preventable illness in Australia, and we know that the right support at the right time can make all the difference.</p><p>Our mission is to empower individuals to make informed decisions about managing nicotine dependency — combining clinical expertise with the convenience of telehealth so that geography, schedule, or stigma never stand in the way of a healthier future.</p>",
            "button": "Learn How It Works",
            "link": "/pages/how-it-works",
            "align": "left"
          }
        }
      },
