            "code": "<div class=\"text-center mt-5 px-lg-4\">\n<h3 class=\"mb-4\">Patient-Centred<br>Care</h3>\n<p>Every treatment plan is personalised because we know a one-size-fits-all approach rarely works for nicotine dependency. Your health goals guide every decision we make.</p>\n</div>",
