            "code": "<div class=\"text-center py-4\">\n<h2 class=\"mb-3\" style=\"color: #fff;\">Ready to Take the First Step?</h2>\n<p style=\"color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 30px;\">Join thousands of Australians who have started their journey toward a smoke-free life with Quity. Our team of registered healthcare professionals is here to guide you every step of the way.</p>\n<a class=\"btn btn-theme\" href=\"/account/register\" style=\"background: #fff; color: #333; padding: 12px 35px; font-weight: 600;\">Apply Now</a>\n</div>",
